metadata.name: The Potting Shed
metadata.description:
The potting shed is a place of restorative work - nurturing plants and connecting with nature. It's good for the soul, too.

The proceeds from this piece will be donated to the Northeast KS YWCA Center for Safety and Empowerment as part of its 2022 Concealed Revealed event.  

The YWCA Center for Safety and Empowerment provides free and confidential services to victims of domestic and sexual violence, stalking, and human trafficking in Shawnee, Jackson, Brown, and Wabaunsee Counties in Kansas, USA.
